{"tid":1009783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本有報警APP,究竟香港有冇報警APP呢?","createTime":"2019-02-05T12:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T12:52:42.000Z","uid":122823,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"0a15d335244eb1f4d08a6b1decd537332e04e396","tid":1009783,"uid":122823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"日本警察廳公佈在明年度引入適用於智能手機的報案系統，此系統將採用 LINE、WhatsApp 等一般人常用的即時傳訊方式，讓罪案被害者受到威脅不能發聲時，又或者報警者是聽覺障礙的人士，都可順利即時聯絡警方。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2018-08-19-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%882.00.22.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2018-08-19-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25882.00.22.png&h=e229709c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現時香港設有電子報案中心，但報案人士不會即時獲得回覆，緊急案件仍需致電 999 熱線。根據 NHK 報道，日本警察廳將在明年度引入即時傳訊方式的手機報警 App。用戶只要按手機，就能與所屬地域的警察本部進行通訊，用戶可利用與 LINE 相似的形式與警方以文字通訊。用戶更可發送相片，而 GPS 定位資訊亦會傳送給警方。警方可掌握準確資料，到達報警人士身處地點。<br />\n<br />\n同樣的 App 已在日本警視廳導入，但受到聽覺障礙者團體多次要求，當地警方將會把有關 App 推展到日本全國。讓聽覺障礙人士，又或者正受到跟蹤、家庭暴力的受害者，在難於發聲的情況下也能順利報警。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2018-08-19-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%882.01.33.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2018-08-19-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25882.01.33.png&h=f876bb81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2018-08-19-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%882.00.43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2018-08-19-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25882.00.43.png&h=5d990988&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/08/19/apppolicejapan/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2Fapppolicejapan%2Flife-tech%2F&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFgomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=cb878168\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/08/19/apppolicejapan/life-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">好多時喺街見到啲人亂泊車,就會1823啦,但佢e-mail又會覆最好報警,究竟香港有冇報警APP呢?</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"04730f8eaab712857a406ebddef10aa73fea1b0c","tid":1009783,"uid":5891,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:30:44.000Z","msg":"香港啲科技嘢，你話呢？"},{"pid":"274f63a49c44d2008abe6298a57ff9a4ff1c3be8","tid":1009783,"uid":174420,"like":4,"dislike":34,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"警務處拎左多1蚊都比本土派咋型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139ccdb0076872b8fe3057112267fc8611ca3021","tid":1009783,"uid":53062,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"274f63a49c44d2008abe6298a57ff9a4ff1c3be8","tid":1009783,"uid":174420,"like":4,"dislike":34,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"警務處拎左多1蚊都比本土派咋型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:36:41.000Z","msg":"警察有邊次撥款俾人阻撓？"},{"pid":"1325f08b6c7987d1031c9c7cfe992050b7b0ac1f","tid":1009783,"uid":3454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:38:04.000Z","msg":"全城報驚撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c0a95d6ad2d6935886b7852338c179bf6a7c49","tid":1009783,"uid":80624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:39:02.000Z","msg":"其實可以sms去992 報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695b30b6d5a15d6e4301f5b417f56d94db9e21e8","tid":1009783,"uid":76793,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:41:21.000Z","msg":"你想靠